<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <p>
      Hi <%= @user.username %>, You are receiving this email because you have
      requested a password reset for your Readit account. Please use this code
      to reset your password: <strong><%= @user.reset_digest %></strong> This code will
      expire one hour from password reset request. To reset your password please
      enter your code in the form here:
      <a href="http://localhost:3001/accountconfirmation">password reset link</a>
      If you did not request your password to be reset please ignore this email
      and your password will stay as it is.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
